<p>
The <%= link_to "outgoing stream", outgoing_stream_path %> manages the sound you provide to this LinkBox and transports it to another LinkBox.
</p>

<p>Use <strong>the same password</strong> in the Incoming Stream setup of the other LinkBox.</p>

<% if (mode ||= nil) == :all or @outgoing_stream.push? %>
<p>
<strong>Network requirements :</strong>
in pull mode, to allow another LinkBox to come and retrieve the stream, you need :
</p>

<ol>
<li>make the port 8000 of this LinkBox accessible <% if @outgoing_stream.local_ip %>(<%= @outgoing_stream.local_ip %>:8000)<% end %> from Internet</li>
<li>use in the Outgoing Stream setup of the other LinkBox, the public address of this LinkBox
<% if @outgoing_stream.public_ip %>(which seems to be <%= @outgoing_stream.public_ip %>)<% end %>
</li>
</ol>

<p>
Read the <%= link_to "LinkBox modes documentation", "http://wiki.tryphon.eu/linkbox/modes" %>. If needed, here is the information detected automatically : 
<ul>
<li>Local address : <%= @outgoing_stream.local_ip or "none" %></li>
<li>Public address : <%= @outgoing_stream.public_ip or "none" %></li>
</p>
<% end %>
